name: Object#003
description:
Another strange ASCII object. It's shape changes according to a variable alpha (values between 0.32 and 1.16), a variable beta (values between 0.32 and 1.16) and a 3D vector (component values between -1.0 and 1.0). Observe and find out what it is like!
Controls: 
- set the value of variable alpha and beta manually or toggle their animation using the ui in the upper right corner
- modify the vector using the ui in the upper right corner 
- control the camera rotation by dragging 
- control the camera zoom by mousewheel or pinch
